.TH "pci_wait_for_pending" 9 "pci_wait_for_pending" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
pci_wait_for_pending \- wait for @mask bit(s) to clear in status word @pos
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" pci_wait_for_pending
.BI "(struct pci_dev *dev "  ","
.BI "int pos "  ","
.BI "u16 mask "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
the PCI device to operate on
.IP "pos" 12
config space offset of status word
.IP "mask" 12
mask of bit(s) to care about in status word
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Return 1 when mask bit(s) in status word clear, 0 otherwise.
